formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	It is the responsibility of management to prepare the financial statement of firm. The firm has prepared financial statement by following the mercantile method of accounting. The promoter has passed all necessary entries in accounts and reported all bank accounts in the financial statements and based on the unaudited accounts produced before us for given this certificate and relied on same for reporting to RERA Authority while certifying Form 3.
2.	The compilation & certification of figures in the said RERA Form - 3 along-with applicable annexure are based & relied on   
Latest Architects & Engineers certificates regarding estimated construction cost, Nos. of Garage/covered/Open parking as per RERA, Calculation of carpet area of each & every units of the said project as per RERA & Percentage of completion of on-site works, 
-	Duly signed plan passed, 
-	Previous years Audited financials, 
-	Duly certified provisional financials up to (30/04/2022), 
-	Duly certified secured and unsecured loans, estimated project cost & receivables from the allottee by the management of entity and; 
-	such other information & explanations provided by the entity & proprietor/partner/director of the Entity, 
which, to the best of our knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
3.	Amount deposited and withdrawn from the bank account reflects only booking receipts collected and utilized in the project.
4.	There are two projects carried out by this partnership firm. The firm has taken project loan in the project name of Shivalik Heights. The land of this project i.e. Elephant Business HUB is given as collateral security hence we have given these details in the project loan in the certificate. However, The firm has not taken any loan in this project hence in Loan Disbursal Received & Loan Repaid and Closing Balance of Loan is not applicable in this case. and details of project loan and loan sanctioned and closing balance already given while giving Form 3 of Shavlik Heights [Rera Registration No is RAA02891]
5.	We clarify that physical copy of Form No.3 & 3A contains certain explanatory and other notes to the various clauses which do not find place in the electronic Form No. 3 & 3A. In view of this, the electronic Form No.3 & 3A should be read together with all the notes appearing in the physical Form No.3 & 3A and in case of any conflict, the information and details provided in physical copy shall prevail.
6.	Management of the entity has provided Customer ID, details of PAN / Aadhar Card, and Mobile Numbers of the allottees, Date of Registered Agreement for sale and Encumbrance Status and we have relied on the same while giving this certificate.
7.	The promoter has directly registered Sale deed instead of agreement for sale registration hence in those cases, we have mentioned the Date of registration of Sale deed in that column.
